  "title": "Trainee Sales Advisor (Fixed Hours, no exp needed!)",
  "description": "<p><em>(Mentorship Provided | No Experience Needed)</em></p><p>Looking to start a meaningful career with growth potential? Join our team as a <strong>Trainee Sales Advisor</strong>. No prior experience? No problem — we provide full training and 1-on-1 mentorship!</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>What You'll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Engage and consult individuals on suitable campaign strategies </li><li>Guide businesses through onboarding and funding options</li><li>Build relationships and support on common FAQ.</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br />✅ Structured mentorship and training<br />✅ Friendly, goal-driven team environment<br />✅ Attractive incentives and career progression<br />✅ Fixed office hours schedule</p><p>Step into a role that’s rewarding, impactful, and full of growth!</p><p><br /><u><strong>📩 Apply now and kickstart your journey with us!</strong></u></p>",
